@node version "Program version"

                                  @{b}XPKPatch@{ub}

  A system patch that makes XPK, PowerPacker and CrunchMania datafiles, as
  well   as   executable   files   crunched   with   XPK  and  PowerPacker
  (as PPLoadSeg), act completely as if they were normal files.

                                @{b}Version 1.8@{ub}

                  Copyright (C) 1996-2000 Grzegorz Krolik

                     Compilation date: 14 October 2000
@endnode

